sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP

    Note over S3,HF: Flow 2a: Model Initialization (startup)
    S3->>HF: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads model files<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    Note over HF: Model loaded into memory<br/>(PyTorch inference ready)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 230)
        Note over Orch,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (Regex/FileType/Custom)
        Orch->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Note over BuiltIn: Local processing:<br/>regex matching,<br/>file-type parsing,<br/>custom Python execution
        BuiltIn-->>Orch: Detection results (JSON)<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 235, 250)
        Note over Orch,HF: Flow 2b: HuggingFace Model Inference
        Orch->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Note over HF: PyTorch inference:<br/>SeqClassification /<br/>TokenClassification /<br/>GraniteForCausalLM
        HF-->>Orch: Classification results (JSON)<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
    end

    rect rgb(250, 240, 230)
        Note over Orch,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
        Orch->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Judge->>vLLM: OpenAI-compatible API call<br/>HTTP (no encryption)
        vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response
        Judge-->>Orch: Judge verdict (JSON)<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
    end
